skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my beatle fact
des: Interested in random facts about The Beatles? 'My Beatle Fact' is a skill that offers you a daily dose of Fab Four history by giving you interesting facts about the Beatles daily. It will be updated often with new records and trivia about the greatest band in the world! What a way to start your faB and gear day! When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests for this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
